sentence.text: Immunohistochemically, tumor cells of all cases were positive for vimentin (100.0%, 60/60), STAT6 (98.3%, 59/60), CD34 (61.7%, 37/60), and the tumor cells were typically positive for CD99, bcl-2, fatty acid beta-oxidation using acyl-CoA dehydrogenase and G protein-coupled receptor signaling pathway as well.Negative for S-100 protein, SOX10, E-cadherin, GFAP.
